    <briefdescription>
<para>The <ref refid="classkukadu_1_1TerminalCostComputer" kindref="compound">TerminalCostComputer</ref> implements the <ref refid="classkukadu_1_1CostComputer" kindref="compound">CostComputer</ref> interface. </para>    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This class implements the <ref refid="classkukadu_1_1CostComputer" kindref="compound">CostComputer</ref> in a simple way. The cost of the last rollout is inserted manually by the user to the console. This method can be used for very low dimensional reinforcement learning as there a low number of rollouts is needed. </para>    </detaileddescription>
